<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>HTML ORDERED LISTS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.csss">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>HTML ORDERED LISTS</h1>
    <div>
      HTML5 ordered lists are used to create an organized list of items:
      The default type attribute for an ordered list is number.
      <ol>
        <li>Nairobi University</li>
        <li>Machakos University</li>
        <li>Kenyatta University</li>
        <li>Kibabii University</li>
      </ol>
      <p>However, you can still specify the type as number.<br>An Ordered list type: number</p>
      <ol type="1">
        <li>Nairobi University</li>
        <li>Machakos University</li>
        <li>Kenyatta University</li>
        <li>Kibabii University</li>
      </ol
      <p>An Ordered list type: roman lowercase</p>
      <ol type="i">
        <li>Nairobi University</li>
        <li>Machakos University</li>
        <li>Kenyatta University</li>
        <li>Kibabii University</li>
      </ol
      <p>An Ordered list type: roman uppercase</p>
      <ol type="I">
        <li>Nairobi University</li>
        <li>Machakos University</li>
        <li>Kenyatta University</li>
        <li>Kibabii University</li>
      </ol>
      <p>An Ordered list type: letters lowercase</p>
      <ol type="a">
        <li>Nairobi University</li>
        <li>Machakos University</li>
        <li>Kenyatta University</li>
        <li>Kibabii University</li>
      </ol>
      <p>An Ordered list type: letters uppercase</p>
      <ol type="A">
        <li>Nairobi University</li>
        <li>Machakos University</li>
        <li>Kenyatta University</li>
        <li>Kibabii University</li>
      </ol>
      <hr>
      <p>We also have a controlled ordered list: These are lists that have a specified starting point.</p>
      <ol type="1" start="4">
        <li>Nairobi University</li>
        <li>Machakos University</li>
        <li>Kenyatta University</li>
        <li>Kibabii University</li>
      </ol>
      <p>HTML nested list:</p>
      <ol type="1" start="1">
        <li>
          Nairobi University:
          <ol type="i">
            <li>School of Medicine</li>
            <li>School of Art</li>
            <li>School of Education</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
          Machakos University
          <ol type="a">
            <li>School of Medicine</li>
            <li>School of Art</li>
            <li>School of Education</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
          Kenyatta University
          <ol type="I">
            <li>School of Medicine</li>
            <li>School of Art</li>
            <li>School of Education</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
          Kibabii University
          <ul list-style-type="disc">
            <li>School of Medicine</li>
            <li>School of Art</li>
            <li>School of Education</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
